          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Final intensities on target of the 43 MeV/A O-18 and",
                "O-20 secondary beams were 2.7*10**4 and 5*10**3 pps",
                "with purities of 98% and 95%, respectively. Two low",
                "pressure multiwire proportional chambers located 1.5",
                "and 0.3 m upstream from the target were used to detect",
                "the incident nuclei."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD",
                "SILI",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The energy and angle of the recoiling",
                "protons were measured using four silicon-strip",
                "detectors, placed at 20 cm from the target, backed by",
                "Si(Li) diodes and CsI crystals read out by photodiodes.",
                "The doubled-sided silicon strip detectors were 6*6 cm2",
                "in size, 300 mu-m thick with 60 strips 1 mm wide on",
                "each side providing for localization in X and Y.",
                "The energy resolution for protons in the silicon strip",
                "detectors was 70 keV, and the angular resolution 0.29",
                "degr."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The telescopes were placed at two settings",
                "covering laboratory angles between 56 and 86 degr.",
                "for the 20O measurements. In the case of 18O, due",
                "to limited beam time, only one setting was used",
                "covering a range between 56 and 72 degr."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "2.3 mg/cm2 polypropylene (C2H)n target located at the",
                "center of the scattering chamber was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute normalization was deduced from the number",
                "of incident nuclei and the target thickness. The error",
                "on the normalization is estimated to be 10% including",
                "the background effect."
              ]
            }
          ],
